<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" >
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>{{orgName}} Sustainability Audit Report</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset */
    body, p, h1, h2, h3, ul {
      margin: 0; padding: 0;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f7f9;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.5;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .company-logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .company-logo img {
      max-height: 100px;
      width: auto;
      height: auto;
    }
    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: #2E5F4D;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .logo img {
      max-height: 80px;
      height: auto;
      width: auto;
      filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
    }
    .grade {
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .grade-icon {
      font-size: 48px;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #2E5F4D;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #276749;
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #D1E7DD;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    ul {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #555555;
    }
    li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #276749;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      padding-top: 15px;
    }
    a {
      color: #276749;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .cta-button {
      background-color: #2E5F4D;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none !important;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    @media (max-width: 620px) {
      body {
        padding: 10px;
      }
      .container {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .grade {
        font-size: 32px;
      }
      .grade-icon {
        font-size: 36px;
      }
      .logo img {
        filter: none;
        max-height: 60px;
      }
      .company-logo img {
        max-height: 80px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header with logo and grade -->
    <div class="header" role="banner">
      <div class="logo" aria-label="Green Orbit Digital logo">
        <img src="http://cdn.mcauto-images-production.sendgrid.net/2ebcdc89e6e3f802/251aaa3a-da8c-4286-a490-57dd2eb3ccfa/500x176.png" alt="Green Orbit Digital Logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="grade" aria-label="Sustainability grade">
        <span class="grade-icon">{{gradeIcon}}</span>
        <span>{{grade}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h1>Sustainability Audit Report</h1>
    <p>Dear <span class="highlight">{{orgName}}</span>,</p>
    <p>We are pleased to share your latest sustainability audit report for your website. This report highlights your website’s environmental performance based on key metrics.</p>

    <h2>Executive Summary</h2>
    <p>{{summary}}</p>

    <h2>Audit Summary</h2>
    <p><strong>Website URL:</strong> <a href="{{url}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{url}}</a></p>
    <p><strong>Grade:</strong> <span class="highlight">{{grade}} — {{gradeInterpretation}}</span></p>

    <h2>Detailed Metrics</h2>
    <p>{{metricsSummary}}</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Estimated CO₂ per page load:</strong> {{co2}} grams</li>
      <li><strong>Total Page Size:</strong> {{totalBytesFormatted}} bytes</li>
      <li><strong>Number of Requests:</strong> {{requestsFormatted}}</li>
      <li><strong>Monthly Estimated CO₂:</strong> {{monthlyCO2kgFormatted}} kg</li>
      <li><strong>Equivalent Car Travel:</strong> {{kmEquivalent}} km</li>
      <li><strong>LED Bulb Powered:</strong> {{bulbHours}} hours</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Root Cause Analysis</h2>
    <ul>
      {{#each rootCauses}}
      <li>{{this}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <h2>Detailed Recommendations</h2>
    <ul>
      {{#each detailedRecommendations}}
      <li><strong>{{priority}} Priority:</strong> {{text}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <h2>Next Steps & Sustainability Goals</h2>
    <ul>
      {{#each nextSteps}}
      <li>{{this}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <h2>Comments</h2>
    <p>{{comments}}</p>

    <!-- CTA Button -->
    <p style="text-align:center;">
      <a href="{{landingPageBaseUrl}}?utm_source={{utmSource}}&amp;utm_medium={{utmMedium}}&amp;utm_campaign={{utmCampaign}}&amp;organization={{orgName}}" class="cta-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Review Your Full Sustainability Roadmap
      </a>
    </p>

    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance implementing these recommendations, please don’t hesitate to contact us.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br/>The Green Orbit Digital Team</p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2025 Green Orbit Digital Ltd. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>